node.text:
…..is somehow oddly satisfying. Seasoned with The Gospel AP. Smoked on the @traegergrills at 250° with hickory. Wrapped around 175° internal when the bark was perfect looking. Topped with brown sugar, Honey Hog Hot & butter in the wrap. Pulled when it was probe tender. 

#MeatChurch #TexasBBQ #PulledPork #TheGospel #Gospel

Texas Twinkies.

Shout out to my dude Tim Hutchins of @hutchins_bbq for the assist since they made em famous.

Video coming soon!

Barbecue at @troyaikman’s house makes for a great Saturday.

I made a March Madness bet with Troy (@alabamambb vs. @uclambb) and had to pay up my loss last night. I gladly cooked for his family + his close friends that he played football with at UCLA. I can’t say enough good things about Troy & his friends. We even got to hear our buddy @stevehelmsband play. Thank you for the hospitality, the jersey that’s headed to @meatchurchbbqsupply and the opportunity Troy!!

Where does the time go? Our littles 1st day back to school today. Sam is going into 3rd grade and Ava Belle is going into 5th grade in her last year at Wilemon STEAM Academy. 

We are so ready for some structure again, so we’re happy they are back with their friends and we can all get back into our routines. I’m most excited that I can actually go eat lunch with them again. At least for now anyway.

We hope everyone has a great and healthy school year!
